Save this script as Create-WinPEBootImage.ps1 and run it as Administrator.

How to Run the Script
Step 1: Save and Run

    1. Copy the script into a text editor and save it as Create-WinPEBootImage.ps1.
    2. Open PowerShell as Administrator.
    3. Navigate to the folder where the script is saved:

	cd C:\Path\To\Script

Run:

    Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force
    .\Create-WinPEBootImage.ps1


